# Markdown math

When writing equations in `.md` files (especially under `literature/`, `writing/`, `course-prep/`):

- Inline math: `$...$` (not `\(...\)`)
- Display math: `$$...$$` on their own lines (not `\[...\]`)

This matches GitHub rendering and common Markdown preview tools.
